62a-9d0f-30359dbd6473"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure></a><p>Apple 现已推出 Vision Pro 开发套件。如果您符合资格，您将获得借用的混合现实耳机以及设置帮助、专家“签到”以及超出开发人员通常获得的额外支持请求。您正在提交申请，而不是购买像旧的 Apple Silicon Developer Transition Kit 这样的产品，因此您需要详细说明现有的应用程序和整体团队人才。该公司将青睐其应用程序“利用”Vision Pro 功能的创作者。苹果还要求开发人员将 Vision Pro 保存在只有授权团队成员才能访问的安全工作空间中。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-developer-kits-are-available-now-181026904.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-our-verdict-on-sonys-newest-noise-canceling-earbuds-111504008.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-our-verdict-on-sonys-newest-noise-canceling-earbuds-111504008.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 263dfe93-dd14-4cfa-8e68-efb91dfe091c</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 11:15:04 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690277290</ingested><modified> 2023-07-25T09:28:16+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ec3bea90-2a1a-11ee-a3ff-6dfd5d74dd57" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-u